          "type": "heading",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Kid's Bed with Metal Gas Lift",
            "heading_size": "h3",
            "heading_h1": false
          }
        },
        "text_3949fT": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>Tidy room, happy kid! Kid’s Bed with a Metal Gas Lift is the perfect blend of smart storage and everyday comfort. Designed to make the most of smaller bedrooms, it lifts effortlessly to reveal a spacious hidden compartment – ideal for storing toys, bedding, clothes, or anything else that needs a home.</p><p>Built with a sturdy metal gas lift mechanism, it’s easy to use and safe for regular access, even for older children.</p>",
            "enlarge_text": false
          }
        }
      },
      "block_order": [
        "heading_t4C6zN",
