        "text_KQ6MME": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>Find the perfect bed frame for your child's room with a range of sizes to choose from, whether it's a small single or a spacious double. Options include 3ft single, 4ft small double, 4'6 double, and even a 5ft king-size bed to suit your needs.</p>",
