          }
        },
        "text_3dJ4id": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>We value your child's safety and, for that reason, include protective side panels with our children's beds. These safety rails prevent your child from falling out of bed. If you select the safety side rails with your kid's bed, then it will come with an 8\" mattress to provide comfort and convenience.</p>",
